FDub Framework
created by: Nick Wallace

Folder Structure:
	data/
		Set of sequential changescripts used to build the schema for the website.
	
	public_html/
		Contains the web root of the project. Point the vhost here.

***INSTALLATION***

Requirements

apache2 php5 mysql-server php5-mcrypt php5-mysql php5-gd php5-imagick php5-xdebug ruby rubygems compass phing

Once those packages are installed please configure config.ini

Run phing configure

Import database - phing dbj

Copy inc/config.template.php to inc/config.php and fill it out

You should be good to go!

***USAGE***

Overall Layout - inc/layouts/default.php

Header - inc/modules/header.php

Footer - inc/modules/footer.php

Javascript Files Include - inc/modules/javascript.php

CSS Files Include - inc/modules/css.php

Main View Files - inc/views/